data.description:
Located in desirable Founder’s Village, this home South facing home welcomes you with an open floorplan and vaulted ceilings.  Enjoy lots of natural light from the many windows throughout, including a picturesque bay window in the front family room. Durable, upgraded flooring on the main and second floors make for low maintenance living. Upstairs you will find 3 large bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, including a primary with ensuite and large walk-in closet. The finished basement with its own half bath makes a great 
home office or 4th bedroom. Outside, the spacious backyard makes a great entertaining space with expanded patio. Founder’s Village is in a great location with easy access to retail, major highways, parks, pickleball courts, and a community pool.
